name: Cherry Garnet Crystal necklace
description:
Whether in a formal gown or casual party dress, this handmade necklace made of matte red Preciosa Czech Crystals is the perfect accessory to make you standout in any crowd.

Handmade by home-based housewives trained by our NGO, Crystal Jewelry necklaces provide a steady source of income and a dignified means of living for the poorest of the poor in the Philippines. Come help us uplift people's lives by being the proud owner of a one of a kind, fashion-forward accessory.

Prices are currently on introductory sale. Buy one today for that special Christmas gift for you or your loved one.
